# App Store Publication Checklist

- [ ] **Preparation**
    - [ ] Verify App Name and Bundle ID
    - [ ] Update Version and Build Number in `pubspec.yaml`
    - [ ] Generate App Icons (various sizes)
    - [ ] specific configuration in `Info.plist` (NSPermissions, etc.)
- [ ] **Apple Developer Account**
    - [ ] Ensure valid Apple Developer Program membership
    - [ ] Create App ID (Identifier)
    - [ ] Create Provisioning Profiles (if manual signing)
- [ ] **App Store Connect**
    - [ ] Create New App in App Store Connect
    - [ ] Fill in App Information (Privacy Policy, Screenshots, etc.)
- [ ] **Build & Release**
    - [ ] Configure Signing in Xcode
    - [ ] Create Flutter Build (`flutter build ios --release`)
    - [ ] Archive in Xcode
    - [ ] Validate and Distribute
